za.ac.wits.elen4010.fluidsim.gui

Class LabelNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • za.ac.wits.elen4010.fluidsim.gui.LabelNode

  • public class LabelNode
extends java.lang.Object
    The label node acts as the highest level of the hierarchy for the TimeCapture class. It has a name and a linked list to data nodes, which store the actual data for the simulat- ion.
    See Also:
    TimeCapture, DataNode
